{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.1","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:1","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.001.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La pri\u00e8re pour tous<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. (1 R 8:48. J\u00e9 29:7. 1 Pi 2:12-15.) (Jn 3:16, 17. H\u00e9 2:9. Mc 16:15, 16.) 1 Jn 3:21, 22.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>J\u2019exhorte donc, avant toutes choses, \u00e0 faire des pri\u00e8res, des supplications, des requ\u00eates, des actions de gr\u00e2ces, pour tous les hommes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.1.20","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.1.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:2","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>pour les rois et pour tous ceux qui sont \u00e9lev\u00e9s en dignit\u00e9, afin que nous menions une vie paisible et tranquille, en toute pi\u00e9t\u00e9 et honn\u00eatet\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:3","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Cela est bon et agr\u00e9able devant Dieu notre Sauveur,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:4","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>qui veut que tous les hommes soient sauv\u00e9s et parviennent \u00e0 la connaissance de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:5","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Car il y a un seul Dieu, et aussi un seul m\u00e9diateur entre Dieu et les hommes, J\u00e9sus-Christ homme,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:6","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>qui s\u2019est donn\u00e9 lui-m\u00eame en ran\u00e7on pour tous. C\u2019est l\u00e0 le t\u00e9moignage rendu en son propre temps,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:7","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>et pour lequel j\u2019ai \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e9tabli pr\u00e9dicateur et ap\u00f4tre, je dis la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, je ne mens pas, charg\u00e9 d\u2019instruire les pa\u00efens dans la foi et la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:8","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Je veux donc que les hommes prient en tout lieu, en \u00e9levant des mains pures, sans col\u00e8re ni mauvaises pens\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:9","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les devoirs des femmes<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-15: cf. 1 Pi 3:1-6. 1 Co 14:34, 35. Tit 2:3-5.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    Je veux aussi que les femmes, v\u00eatues d\u2019une mani\u00e8re d\u00e9cente, avec pudeur et modestie, ne se parent ni de tresses, ni d\u2019or, ni de perles, ni d\u2019habits somptueux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:10","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>mais qu\u2019elles se parent de bonnes \u0153uvres, comme il convient \u00e0 des femmes qui font profession de servir Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:11","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Que la femme \u00e9coute l\u2019instruction en silence, avec une enti\u00e8re soumission.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:12","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Je ne permets pas \u00e0 la femme d\u2019enseigner, ni de prendre de l\u2019autorit\u00e9 sur l\u2019homme; mais elle doit demeurer dans le silence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:13","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Car Adam a \u00e9t\u00e9 form\u00e9 le premier, Eve ensuite;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:14","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>et ce n\u2019est pas Adam qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 s\u00e9duit, c\u2019est la femme qui, s\u00e9duite, s\u2019est rendue coupable de transgression.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:15","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Elle sera n\u00e9anmoins sauv\u00e9e en devenant m\u00e8re, si elle pers\u00e9v\u00e8re avec modestie dans la foi, dans la charit\u00e9, et dans la saintet\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbce349f9.63117437');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbce349f9.63117437\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbce349f9.63117437","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbce349f9.63117437'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbce349f9.63117437\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}